ActNational Energy Board Act
National Energy Board Act Part VI (Oil and Gas) Regulations
SubjectIssuance of Licence GL-327 - Cedar 1 LNG Export Ltd.
PrecisOrder approving the ISSUANCE OF LICENCE GL-327 to Cedar 1 LNG Export Ltd. to export natural gas, in the form of liquefied natural gas, from a point at the outlet of the loading arm of the natural gas liquefaction terminals to be located in the Northern Douglas Channel in the vicinity of Kitimat, British Columbia.
